Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like having to do this\Nto elderly people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're very important witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you dying\Nor running away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've barricaded the back door\Nand most of the windows with furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure if someone wanted to,\Nthey could easily get through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't the two of us\Nget downstairs now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to shoot a gun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have anything happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You will survive this\Nand expose the whole truth to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim, you stay in here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if something\Nhappens to you, Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be all right. I've got\Na powerful friend who will help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can be assured of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm in a pinch,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,he comes and helps me\Nno matter where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He never lets any evil deed go unpunished.\NHe's the invincible Magnificent Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:04.08,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\\pos(728,754)}The Magnificent Steiner's Rage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the trail north!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we've gotten\Nmost of the children out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You go too! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't looked\Naround the center of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave that to me.\NI want you to guide everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one question!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know a man named Bonaparta…\NI mean, Klaus Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he owns the Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be frightened. I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to escape as fast as I could…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but the town is filled with bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where to run to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you escape from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's… giving orders from his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard him talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was weird because\Nhe kept going in and out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He showered and changed\Nevery time he came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this Roberto now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A room on the fourth floor\Nof Hotel Bergbach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:05:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he was that kind of guy. I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Some people are hiding\Nat the other hotel, Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get there alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone? I'm too scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This trip of fantasy\Nhas become one of reality at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the real person\Nthat is you has arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,my vacation of tracking this thread\Nof fantasy has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on,\NI'm working as a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to get back on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this girl with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The person you're after is\Nat Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have plenty of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories… They're becoming clearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that were most deeply hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your most deeply hidden memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones I never wanted to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If these memories…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If Johan remembers these same things…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from this town. Please don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the man giving orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you, where's Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stand up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!\NThere are dead people everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lose my mind if I stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you have to go\Nto Hotel Versteck as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife… Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but your wife is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here.\NYou've got to get somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill whoever it was who killed Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and give me your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill whoever it was\Nwho destroyed our happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't what your wife\Nwould have wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife would've wanted\Nyour child to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the trail.\NYou can escape to the north on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come with us.\NForget about going to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't want to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll be back soon. Stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's not me and my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,these people are after\Nbecause we won the lottery, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. These last few days have\Nfelt like a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I bought all these guns\Nbecause of all that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal life is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell my wife\Nthis wasn't our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Heinich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Heinich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My… wife…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Heinich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're shooting\Nfrom the building across the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this hotel have a basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a storage room under the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hanging in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? What about you, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's out of liquor,\Nso he lost his mind and is doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:13:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's gone crazy like he does\Nwhen he hits me every day. Dad's…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think your dad's\Nthe kind of person who'd do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I... if I went out there,\Nsurely this would all end…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way in hell\NI'm letting you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep talking like that,\NI'll tie you up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here. I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When in a real bind, the invincible\NMagnificent Steiner shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw examples of that\Nin my experiments long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When faced with the massive stress\Nof overwhelming anger or sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the children would manifest\Na different personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children would be\Nexcessively violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and most of them would kill themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you've survived so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I'm unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who ordered you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to me if you're people\Nfrom the former Eastern Bloc,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you're ex-secret police,\Nor whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm just a nobody from nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to someone's orders!\NListen to your own heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Think long and hard\Nabout what you're doing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so afraid, but I made it here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magnificent Steiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be glued to the TV\Nwatching it every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have no memory of the final episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,…just call my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the young man\Nwho was the weakling main character
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,realized that he transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,into the Magnificent Steiner\Nwhen overcome with anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the young man found happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That young man…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that young man ever find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a little farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more\Nand we'll be out of the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're people from Ruhenheim, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is happening in town,\Nisn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people with guns entered\Nand started a massacre around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not part of them, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. We're on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there an Asian?\NDid you see a Japanese man with long hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you friends of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He did everything he could\Nto get these children out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still there now\Ntrying to help the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I left him,\Nhe was headed to Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My car is at the end of the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it to take the injured\Nand sick to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And contact the police\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two going to town?\NYou shouldn't! You'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma… The Asian man, he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to save him.\NNow hurry and contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi… I thought you'd come, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Two in the building next door…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One downstairs… and one in here…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed four in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Magnificent Steiner showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he never showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I did this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I let my anger take over\Nand did it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to check that wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I forget… Here, a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he found it\Nat the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone to Hotel Bergbach alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, you need--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me… relax here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is raining a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much nicer\Naround here when it's sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When the weather clears up,\Nlet's take Wim here with us for a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring along\Nsome delicious wine and delicious cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sad because I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my child died…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,People cannot lose their emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My emotions… got lost somewhere inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like a letter I sent to myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that took decades to finally arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how true sadness feels…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or is this… happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In the final episode…\Nof The Magnificent Steiner…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,he probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,turned back... into a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I…
